De_cmd_arena

Made by: kaos4u

Contact info: kaos4u@gmail.com

Date:  06/04/08

File size: 14.3 MB

Spawn points: 40+

====================================

This map was made for the CmD clan.  The Letters "CMD" were made into hallways, then connected together along with
a few other rooms of 3 different hight levels to make a battle arena with 2 bombsites.  There are many different 
routes to get around the map.  This version is kind of plain, and was put together to test game play.  A later version
may be in the works, that will include a theme more detail, and some repairs to brush work.  

features:  

2 bombsites
buyzones
mini map overview
an easter egg or two
